name: S TO F!
description:
Start to Finish
Begin at the starting point and work your way towards the end!

If you encounter challenges along the way, don’t worry.
There will be soft music playing to energize you.


Features

- There are more than 60 stages.
- Game Center
- It comes with nice music.
- There will be regular addition of stages.
- There will also be free content except for those, which are ad-free.
